      <title>六张图表告诉你英国今年的糟糕开局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/uk-bond-yields-borrowing-costs-ramp-up-pressure-on-rachel-reeves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对英国财政状况感到担忧，英国资产在新年伊始遭遇了可怕的开局，这再次唤起了人们对 2022 年导致前首相利兹·特拉斯下台的市场危机的记忆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/uk-bond-yields-borrowing-costs-ramp-up-pressure-on-rachel-reeves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>玛氏公司筹集 10 亿美元私人债务，为发行更大规模债券做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/mars-raises-1-billion-private-debt-in-prelude-to-larger-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，玛氏公司 (Mars Inc.) 正通过私募债券借入相当于 10 亿美元的资金，开始偿还为收购食品制造商 Kellanova 而借入的银行贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/mars-raises-1-billion-private-debt-in-prelude-to-larger-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:19:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球动荡下，印度债券资金外流创 2020 年以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/india-sees-most-bond-outflows-since-2020-amid-global-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对持续通胀的担忧，全球债券市场出现抛售，海外投资者以疫情爆发以来未曾见过的速度抛售印度债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/india-sees-most-bond-outflows-since-2020-amid-global-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:12:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗策略师表示，到 2025 年底全球股市将上涨 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/global-stocks-to-rally-10-by-end-2025-citi-strategists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团策略师表示，受企业盈利强劲增长和美国以外地区股市上涨推动，今年全球股市可能上涨 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/global-stocks-to-rally-10-by-end-2025-citi-strategists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:05:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场动荡后，太平洋投资管理公司 (Pimco) 和富达投资 (Fidelity) 坚持押注英国政府债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/fidelity-pimco-stick-with-uk-gilt-bets-after-market-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[太平洋投资管理公司、富兰克林邓普顿和富达国际等投资者在本周暴跌后仍坚持押注英国政府债券，其中一些投资者还希望购买更多债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/fidelity-pimco-stick-with-uk-gilt-bets-after-market-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 08:33:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金连续第四天上涨，关注美国就业数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/gold-steady-after-three-day-gain-gain-with-us-payrolls-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商等待美国就业数据的公布，黄金价格连续第四天上涨，这将有助于决定美联储今年的政策前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/gold-steady-after-three-day-gain-gain-with-us-payrolls-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 00:36:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寒流导致库存紧张，油价跃升至三个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受严寒冬季天气影响，美国原油库存再次下降，反映出全球市场趋紧，油价上涨至三个月高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 23:30:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国债券纠纷可能导致英国央行降息计划失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/bond-turmoil-raises-prospect-of-slower-bank-of-england-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，英国的市场动荡使人们关注点集中在工党政府身上，但经济学家表示，英国央行也必须减缓降息步伐，以应对这一挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/bond-turmoil-raises-prospect-of-slower-bank-of-england-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冰冻天气挤压电力市场，英国风力发电量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uk-power-market-set-to-remain-tight-on-cold-windless-weather</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于气温骤降导致价格上涨，英国电力市场预计将于本周六迎来两周以来的最低风电发电量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/uk-power-market-set-to-remain-tight-on-cold-windless-weather</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 18:10:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
